      "2_player_game_place_discs_that_show_ra": "Kukure in ruo ri-kukure. Likūt disc ko rej kwaḷọk ṃōttan ko rejjab jeḷā ilo grid 7×6. Ṃōṇōṇō in ṇaetan ṃōttan.",
