      "daily_routine_templates": "⏱ Template in jerbal in raan otemjej",
      "pre_built_sequences_of_activities_that": "Laajrak in jerbal ko eṃōj kōṃṃani ṃokta me rej ekkar ñan block in awa (10 minute, 30 minute, 45 minute). Kāālōt juon im ḷoore.",
      "identify_fractions_2": "Kile ṃōttan",
