      "exit_ticket_generator": "🎫 Ri-kōṃṃan tiket in diwōj",
      "generate_a_3_question_exit_ticket_on_t": "Kōṃṃan juon tiket in diwōj in 3-kajjitōk ioon topic eo ej kab katakin. Pri im leḷọk ilo jeṃḷọk in katak.",
      "topic_2": "Topic",
      "generate_and_print_exit_ticket": "🖨 Kōṃṃan im pri tiket in diwōj",
      "grade_3_fraction_assessment_checklist": "Checklist in Assessment in Ṃōttan Kilaaj 3",
      "grade_4_fraction_assessment_checklist": "Checklist in Assessment in Ṃōttan Kilaaj 4",
      "grade_5_fraction_assessment_checklist": "Checklist in Assessment in Ṃōttan Kilaaj 5",
      "assessment_checklist": "☑ Checklist in assessment",
      "per_grade_skills_checklists_use_during": "Checklist in kapeel in kajjojo kilaaj. Kōjerbal ilo iien assessment juon-ñan-juon ak ñan karōk katak.",
      "my_child_says_i_hate_fractions": "Nejū ej ba \"Ijdike ṃōttan\"",
      "very_common_fractions_break_the_rules_": "Eḷap an waḷọk. Ṃōttan rej rupe kien ko ri-katak rej katak ñan nōṃba iio — nōṃba reḷap rejjab aolep iien meḷeḷe eo joñan reḷap. Illu eo ej ṃool im ekkar. Jipañ kōn: (1) kōjerbal model alikkar āinwōt pizza ak strip in ṃōttan, (2) kōpooḷ ñan mour ilijjukwi (kōmat, awa, jāān), (3) kaṃṃinene iiet im elōñ alen (5 minute ilo raan) jān session eaetok, (4) nōbar kate, jab uwaak rejiṃwe wōt.",
      "my_child_doesn_t_understand_why_proced": "Nejū ejjab meḷeḷe ETKE procedure rej jerbal",
      "they_are_not_alone_most_students_learn": "Rejjab make iaer — enañin aolep ri-katak rej katak procedure ṃokta im unin tokālik. Jipañ kōn kwaḷọk aolep iien wāween eo procedure ej wāween ippān pija. \"Koorḷọk 3/4 kōn 1/2\" emaroñ jeje āinwōt rectangle. Tab in Op Proofs ej kōṃṃane ñan eok. Kajjitōk \"etke?\" ilo jouj im elōñ alen.",
      "how_can_i_help_with_homework_without_d": "Ewi wāween in jipañ homework ilo jab kōṃṃane ñan er?",
      "use_the_worked_examples_tab_they_show_": "Kōjerbal tab in Worked Examples — rej kwaḷọk procedure jekjek-ilọk-jekjek kōn ḷōmṇak. Etetal ilo apañ rejejjo ippān doon, jab eo wōt juon. Ñe rej ba \"Ijaje ewi wāween jino,\" kajjitōk \"Ta eo apañ ej kajjitōk bwe kwōn pukot? Ta eo jej jeḷā?\" System in hint ilo Word Problems ej leḷọk hint elōñ layer — kajjioñ eo ṃokta ṃokta jān uwaak.",
      "what_should_i_drill": "Ta eo in aikuj kaṃṃinene?",
      "ies_practice_guide_recommends_1_magnit": "IES Practice Guide ej rojak: (1) ḷōmṇak in joñan (jerbal in line in nōṃba), (2) kōtaan in alikkar im symbolic, (3) apañ in naan ilo context. KŌJPARŌK: kaṃṃinene procedure ilo ejjeḷọk meḷeḷe. Kōjerbal 5 minute ilo Benchmark Trainer, 5 ilo Word Problems, im 5 ilo kukure — eñin ej session in 15-minute eṃṃan.",
      "my_child_gets_the_procedure_right_but_": "Nejū ej kōṃṃan procedure jiṃwe ak uwaak ebōd",
      "usually_means_a_small_arithmetic_error": "Enañin aolep iien meḷeḷe eo ej bōd in math edik (āinwōt koorḷọk bōd) ak ejjab kapidodo. Kwaḷọk Cheat Sheet ñan er — remaroñ etale jerbal eo aer jekjek-ilọk-jekjek. Rōjañ er ñan kaṃool kōn wāween eo juon (kōttōbalbal ṃokta, ak kōjerbal model eo juon).",
      "what_if_i_don_t_remember_fractions_wel": "Ta ñe ña make ijjab keememej ṃōttan eṃṃan?",
      "you_don_t_have_to_be_the_expert_use_th": "Kwōjjab aikuj in ri-jeḷā! Kōjerbal Tab Guide im Worked Examples — rej kōmelele procedure alikkar. Eṃṃanḷọk: kwaḷọk \"jen jeḷā men in ippān doon.\" Kwōmaroñ katak ippān nejūṃ. Tab in Vocabulary ej jipañ barāinwōt ñan rūtto.",
      "how_do_i_know_if_my_child_is_on_track": "Ewi wāween in jeḷā eḷaññe nejū ej pād ilo iaḷ eo?",
