      "let_your_number_be_n_the_sequence_n_1_": "Kōṃṃan bwe nōṃba eo aṃ en n. Laajrak eo: (n+1) × 2 + 4 − 6 = 2n + 2 + 4 − 6 = 2n. Ajej kōn 2 → n. Bōkḷọk eo jinointata → 0. Kōttar — eñin ej leḷọk 0, jab 1. Kajjioñ: n → (n+1)×2 = 2n+2 → +4 = 2n+6 → −6 = 2n → ÷2 = n → −jinointata = 0. \"Ṃoṇ\" eo ej pedped ioon constant ko rej ṇooj ilo laajrak.",
