      "the_harmonic_series": "Series in harmonic",
      "even_though_each_term_is_small_the_ser": "Meñe kajjojo naan edik, series eo ej depakpakḷọk. Ñan eḷḷā jān 100, kwōj aikuj tarrin 1.5 × 10^43 naan. Men in eṃōj kaṃoole kōn Nicole Oresme ilo iiō 1300 ko kōn kōjerbal koba: 1/3 + 1/4 > 1/4 + 1/4 = 1/2; 1/5+...+1/8 > 4 × 1/8 = 1/2; kwōmaroñ aolep iien pukot bar juon 1/2 ñan koba.",
      "farey_sequences": "Laajrak in Farey",
      "check_1_4_and_1_3_4_1_1_3_1_check_2_5_": "Etale 1/4 im 1/3: (4)(1) − (1)(3) = 1. Etale 2/5 im 1/2: (5)(1) − (2)(2) = 1. Kadkad in ej kōṃṃan wōjke in Stern-Brocot in aolep nōṃba rational.",
