      "kicks_use_a_sine_oscillator_with_a_pit": "Kicks rej kōjerbal juon sine oscillator ippān pitch sweep. Snares rej koba noise (filtered) + tone body. Hi-hats rej kōjerbal high-pass filtered noise bursts.",
      "4_4_4_quarter_note_beats_per_bar_most_": "4/4 = 4 quarter-note beats ilo juon bar (eḷaptata). 3/4 = eñjake in waltz. 6/8 = compound duple. 5/4 im 7/8 rej kōṃṃan grooves rejjab jejjet, rej oktak.",
      "keys_arranged_by_ascending_5ths_clockw": "Keys rej karōki kōn 5ths rej wanlōñḷọk ilo iaḷ in awa. Keys rej epaake doon rej jejaake 6 iaan 7 note. Etal ilo iaḷ in awa ej kobaik sharps; oktak jān awa ej kobaik flats.",
      "every_musical_sound_contains_overtones": "Kajjojo ainikien music ewōr overtones ilōñin fundamental eo. Kajoor ko aer relative rej pepe kake timbre — eñin unin trumpet ej āinjuon jān flute ilo ejja pitch eo wōt.",
      "an_interval_is_the_distance_between_tw": "Juon interval ej tolọk ikōtaan ruo pitch, joñe ilo semitones. Frequency ratio ej pepe consonance (ratios rejjabmāālel āinwōt 3:2 rej roñ eṃṃan).",
      "plays_chord_notes_one_at_a_time_in_seq": "Ej kōjañ note ko in chord juon-juon ilo laajrak. Lōñ = jān lōñ ñan lōñ, Laḷ = jān lōñ ñan laḷ. Ej kōṃṃan patterns rej tọọr jān chords rej jutak.",
      "a_filter_removes_frequencies_above_low": "Juon filter ej joḷọk frequencies ko ilōñin (lowpass), iumwin (highpass), ak iturin (bandpass) juon cutoff frequency. Resonance (Q) ej kaḷapḷọk frequencies epaake cutoff, ej kōṃṃan juon peak.",
      "tremolo_periodic_volume_changes_amplit": "Tremolo: oktak in volume iien ñan iien (amplitude modulation). Vibrato: oktak in pitch iien ñan iien (frequency modulation). Erruo rej kōṃṃakūt jān juon LFO (Low Frequency Oscillator).",
      "discovered_in_1983_a_noise_burst_feeds": " Eṃōj lo e ilo 1983. Juon noise burst ej deḷọñ ilo juon delay line ekadu potata ippān feedback. Delay time ej pepe pitch. Juon filter ilo feedback loop ej kōṃṃakūt meram im decay. Ej kajjioñe plucked strings ilo wāween jidik.",
      "the_sequencer_is_a_composition_tool_ea": "Sequencer ej juon kein jerbal in composition. Kajjojo step ej jutak kōn juon subdivision in beat. Melody row ej likūt pitched notes, drums rej kobaik rhythm. Musical notation ej kwaḷọk ta eo kwōj kōṃṃane.",
      "notes_on_lines_and_spaces_represent_pi": "Note ko ilo line im space rej jutak kōn pitch. Duration ej walọk jān wāween note: whole (○), half (𝅗𝅥), quarter (♩), eighth (♪). Staff ewōr 5 line.",
