      "play_piano_keys_presets": "Kōjañ — piano keys + presets",
      "equal_temperament_12_notes_per_octave_": "Equal temperament: 12 note ilo juon octave, ratio 2^(1/12). A4 = 440 Hz; A5 = 880 Hz. Well-Tempered Clavier an Bach (1722) ear kareel laḷ in kōn compromise in. Kajjojo note kwōj kōjañe ijin ej pād ioon grid eo.",
      "scales_the_major_minor_modal_grammar": "Scales — grammar in major + minor + modal",
      "major_w_w_h_w_w_w_h_minor_w_h_w_w_h_w_": "Major: W-W-H-W-W-W-H. Minor: W-H-W-W-H-W-W. 7 modes (Ionian, Dorian, Phrygian, Lydian, Mixolydian, Aeolian, Locrian) rej itok jān oktak in interval pattern in major scale.",
      "chords_stacked_thirds_inversions": "Chords — stacked thirds + inversions",
      "triads_root_third_fifth_major_4_3_semi": "Triads: root + third + fifth. Major (4+3 semitones), minor (3+4), diminished (3+3), augmented (4+4). 7th chords rej kobaik bar juon third. Music pop = ~6 chords rej bar kōṃṃani; jazz ej kōjerbal extensions im substitutions.",
      "harmony_pad_voiced_pads_drones": "Harmony Pad — voiced pads + drones",
      "sustained_chord_textures_the_bed_under": "Sustained chord textures — bed eo iumwin enañin aolep cinematic score. Kajjioñ iv-V-i ilo minor, ak i-VI-VII ñan eñjake in Hans Zimmer. Drones ilo fifths rej rejetak music classical in India im ṃanit ko in bagpipe.",
      "beat_pad_sample_based_drums": "Beat Pad — sample-based drums",
      "most_popular_music_sits_at_4_4_90_130_": "Elōñ music ko rej buñbuñ rej pād ilo 4/4, 90-130 BPM. Hip-hop ~85-95, house 120-130, drum-and-bass ~170 (eñjake in half-time). Kick ilo 1+3, snare ilo 2+4 = backbeat — foundation in rock + pop.",
      "theory_the_math_behind_the_sound": "Theory — math eo ālikin ainikien",
      "pythagoras_500_bce_discovered_consonan": "Pythagoras (~500 BCE) ear lo consonance jān integer frequency ratios: octave 2:1, fifth 3:2, fourth 4:3. Helmholtz ear kaḷapḷọk men in ilo 1862. Ainikien = compression waves; music = patterns jaar errā ñan ba reaiboojoj.",
