      "fm_synthesis_controls": "🌟 FM Synthesis Controls",
      "fm_synthesis_2": "FM Synthesis",
      "frequency_modulation_fm_synthesis_uses": "Frequency Modulation (FM) synthesis ej kōjerbal juon oscillator (modulator) ñan ukōt frequency in bar juon (carrier) ṃōkaj. Ratio in modulator:carrier ej pepe harmonic content. Ratios rejjab pen (1:1, 2:1, 3:1) rej kōṃṃan harmonic tones. Ratios rej pen rej kōṃṃan metallic, bell-like, ak inharmonic sounds. Yamaha DX7 ear kōṃṃan bwe FM en buñbuñ ilo 1983.",
      "bright": "Meram",
      "fm_mod_depth": "FM modulation depth",
