      "supersaw_controls": "⚡ SuperSaw Controls",
      "supersaw_unison": "SuperSaw / Unison",
      "supersaw_stacks_multiple_sawtooth_osci": "SuperSaw ej kobaik elōñ sawtooth oscillators rejjidik detune jān doon. Men in ej kōṃṃan juon ainikien eḷap, depakpak, ej romaak — kōkaḷḷe in EDM, trance, im pop in raan kein. Elōñḷọk voices = mijeljeḷ ak ej kōjerbal elōñḷọk CPU. Detuning ej kōṃṃakūt joñan an voices tutu ettoḷọk ilo tuning — elōñ detune = depakpak/āinwōt chorus, iiet = kilep/lukkuun.",
