      "arpeggiator_gate": "Gate in arpeggiator",
      "an_arpeggiator_plays_the_notes_of_a_ch": "🔬 Juon arpeggiator ej kōjañ note ko in chord juon-juon ilo laajrak. \"Lōñ\" ej etal jān laḷ ñan lōñ, ej kōṃṃan kajoor ej wanlōñ. \"Laḷ\" ej wanlaḷ ñan eñjake in wōtlọk in dān. Ṃōkaj ej kōṃṃakūt speed (dik = ṃōkaj). Gate ej kōṃṃakūt joñan an kajjojo note jañ (100% = legato, 10% = staccato). Kajjioñ ṃōkaj=100ms + 4 octaves + up pattern ñan classic trance arp!",
      "live_mic_effects_lab": "🎤 Live Mic Effects Lab",
      "sing_speak_or_play_an_instrument_hear_": "Al, kōnono, ak kōjañ juon instrument — roñjake effects ilo iien eo!",
      "monitor_hear_yourself_use_headphones": "🔊 Monitor (roñjake eok make — kōjerbal headphones!)",
      "microphone_monitor_volume": "Volume in monitor in microphone",
      "how_effects_change_sound_waves": "🔬 Ewi Wāween Effects Rej Ukōt Sound Waves",
      "filter_cutoff": "Filter (Cutoff)",
      "removes_frequencies_above_lowpass_or_b": "Ej joḷọk frequencies ko ilōñin (lowpass) ak iumwin (highpass) juon threshold. Āinwōt kobaik pā ioon lọñiṃ — frequencies ko relōñ rej jako, ainikien ej erom \"marok\" ḷapḷọk.",
      "delay": "Delay",
      "creates_echoes_by_copying_the_signal_a": "Ej kōṃṃan echoes jān copye signal im bar kōjañe ālikin juon iien ekadu. Feedback ej kōṃṃakūt oran echoes rej bar walọk.",
      "reverb_2": "Reverb",
      "simulates_room_acoustics_by_creating_t": "Ej kajjioñe acoustics in juon room jān kōṃṃan tọujin echoes redik rej koba ippān doon. Room edik = reverb ekadu, cathedral = reverb aetok.",
      "distortion": "Distortion",
      "clips_the_waveform_peaks_turning_smoot": "Ej bukwe peaks in waveform, ukōt sine waves remera ñan wāween repen, ewōr kona. Men in ej kobaik harmonics rekāāl ko rejjab pād ilo ainikien eo ṃokta.",
      "chorus": "Chorus",
      "duplicates_the_signal_with_a_slight_co": "Ej copye signal ippān juon delay edik ej oktak wōt. Men in ej kajjioñe elōñ voices/instruments rej kōjañ ippān doon jab lukkuun jiṃor.",
      "tremolo": "Tremolo",
      "rapidly_varies_the_volume_up_and_down_": "Ej ukōt volume lōñ im laḷ ṃōkaj, ej kōṃṃan juon effect ej iddik. Ekkā ilo surf guitar im music in organ.",
      "use_headphones_when_monitoring_to_avoi": "Kōjerbal headphones ñe kwōj monitoring ñan bōprae feedback loops! Mic ej etal iloan aolep effects ko ilōñ (filter, delay, reverb, im bar jet) — karōki bwe kwōn roñjake ewi wāween kajjojo ej ukōt ainikieṃ ak instrument eo aṃ.",
      "connect_your_microphone_to_run_your_vo": "Kobaik microphone eo aṃ ñan tōl ainikieṃ ak instrument eo aṃ iloan effects chain ilo iien eo.",
      "see_your_voice_as_a_waveform_frequency": "Lo ainikieṃ āinwōt waveform + frequency spectrum. Roñjake ewi wāween filter, delay, reverb, distortion, im chorus rej ukōt sound waves ilo ānbwin.",
      "xy_performance_pad": "🎯 XY Performance Pad",
      "touch_drag_x_pitch_y_filter_effect": "Uññūr & iper — X = pitch, Y = filter/effect",
      "xy_pad_performance": "XY Pad Performance",
      "the_xy_pad_maps_your_finger_mouse_posi": "XY pad ej map jikin addiin peiṃ/mouse ñan musical parameters ilo iien eo. X axis ej kōṃṃakūt pitch (anmiiñ = laḷ, anmooṇ = lōñ). Y axis ej kōṃṃakūt filter cutoff frequency (lōñ = meram, laḷ = marok). Men in ej āinwōt instruments āinwōt Korg Kaoss Pad, eo ear ukōt live electronic music performance jān ukōt 2D gestures ñan ainikien.",
      "xy_performance_pad_left_right_is_pitch": "XY performance pad. Anmiiñ–anmooṇ ej pitch, lōñ–laḷ ej filter brightness. Kōjerbal arrow keys ñan eṃṃakūt im kōjañ juon note; kalikūt Escape ak Space ñan bōjrak.",
