      "chord_progressions_create_emotional_jo": "Chord progressions rej kōṃṃan iaḷ ko in eñjake. Chord I (tonic) ej eñjake āinwōt 'ṃweo iṃō.' Chord V (dominant) ej kōṃṃan tension eo ekōṇaan bar rọọl ñan I. Chord vi (relative minor) ej kobaik būroṃōj ak mwilaḷ. Chord IV (subdominant) ej eṃṃakūt ettoḷọk jān ṃweo iṃō ilo jouj. Rej ḷōmṇak bwe progression I-V-vi-IV ej walọk ilo eḷapḷọk jān 70% in al ko in pop kōnke ej kajjidik eñjake kein reṃṃan.",
      "roman_numerals_i_ii_iii_iv_v_vi_vii_re": "Roman numerals (I, ii, iii, IV, V, vi, vii°) rej jutak kōn degree ko in scale. Leta eḷap = major chord. Leta edik = minor chord.",
