      "tilted_59_from_rotation_axis_off_cente": "Ej jeplōklōk 59° jān jikin an doulul! Ejjab pād ilo lukwōn. Juon wāween ejjab āinwōt jabdewōt.",
      "also_highly_tilted_47_and_off_center_c": "Barāinwōt ej jeplōklōk eḷap (47°) im ejjab pād ilo lukwōn. Juon jikin magnet epen meḷeḷe.",
      "too_small_and_cold_for_a_dynamo_no_pro": "Edikḷọk im epiọ ñan juon dynamo. Ejjeḷọk kōjparok jān kōto in aḷ.",
      "venus_has_a_runaway_greenhouse_effect_": "Venus ewōr an greenhouse effect ejjab bōjrak eo ej tōpar 462°C!",
      "saturn_has_146_known_moons_as_of_2024": "Saturn ewōr 293 allōñ jejeḷā kake ilo lajrak in dayax-gacmeed an JPL kiiō.",
      "uranus_has_an_axial_tilt_of_97_77": "Uranus ej jeplōklōk 97.77° jān jikin an doulul!",
      "mercury_is_only_4_879_km_in_diameter": "Mercury depakpakin ej 4,879 km wōt.",
      "pluto_takes_248_earth_years_to_orbit_t": "Pluto ej bōk 248 iiō in Laḷ ñan doulul Aḷ juon alen!",
      "jupiter_rotates_in_just_10_hours": "Jupiter ej doulul ilo 10 awa wōt!",
      "iron_oxide_rust_gives_mars_its_red_col": "Iron oxide (jerbal in ṃor) ej leḷọk ñan Mars kōḷōr būrōrō eo an.",
      "saturn_s_density_is_less_than_water_0_": "Eddo in Saturn edikḷọk jān dān (0.687 g/cm³)!",
      "olympus_mons_on_mars_is_21_9_km_high_n": "Olympus Mons ioon Mars ej 21.9 km utiej — enañin 3 alen jān Everest!",
      "neptune_s_winds_reach_2_100_km_h": "Kōto ko an Neptune rej tōpar 2,100 km/h!",
      "earth_s_magnetic_field_deflects_charge": "Bukwōn magnet an Laḷ ej kōjepḷaak menin aḷ ko rewōr charge. Ozone ej jipañ kōn UV, ak magnetosphere eo ej likōkḷaḷ eḷaptata!",
      "the_iau_s_2006_definition_requires_pla": "Naan in kōmeḷeḷe an IAU ilo 2006 ej aikuj bwe planet ren karreoiki iaḷ in doulul eo aer jān menin ko jet.",
      "also_called_the_goldilocks_zone_not_to": "Barāinwōt rej ba \"Goldilocks zone\" — ejjab māāṇāṇ otem māāṇāṇ, ejjab piọ otem piọ, bwe dān en dān ioon.",
      "the_moon_rotates_exactly_once_per_orbi": "Allōñ ej ukōt make juon alen ilo juon doulul — lokjak in ej waḷọk jān kajoor in ibwijleplep ilo bilien iiō.",
      "opportunity_rover_found_hematite_blueb": "Rover eo Opportunity ear lo \"blueberry\" in hematite — dekā ko rej waḷọk wōt ilo dān. Pija ko jān mejatoto rej kwaḷọk delta in river ko ṃor!",
      "venus_is_hotter_462_c_vs_430_c_mercury": "Venus emāāṇāṇḷọk (462°C ippān 430°C)! Ejjeḷọk an Mercury mejatoto ñan dāpij māāṇāṇ. Greenhouse effect eo eḷapḷọk tokjān jān tōḷọk.",
      "gas_giants_have_no_solid_surface_they_": "Ejjeḷọk an gas giant ko ioon epen! Rej eḷaptata hydrogen im helium gas eo ej eddoḷọk wōt ñan lukwōn eo. Juon probe enaaj wanlaḷḷọk im ejjeḷọk jeṃḷọken.",
      "earth_s_distance_from_the_sun_doesn_t_": "Tōḷọk an Laḷ jān Aḷ ejjab oktak ilo raan. Raelep ej meḷeḷein bwe Aḷ ej utiejtata ilo mejatoto eo aṃ. Laḷ epaaktata ilo Jānwōde (perihelion)!",
      "jupiter_is_11x_wider_than_earth_and_1_": "Jupiter ej 11 alen depakpakḷọk jān Laḷ, im 1,300 Laḷ remaroñ deḷọñ ilowaan! Solar system ewōr an āinjuon eḷap ilo joñan.",
      "pluto_is_still_in_the_solar_system_it_": "Pluto ej pād wōt ilo solar system! Raar ukōt jān \"planet\" ñan \"dwarf planet\" ilo 2006, ak ej doulul wōt Aḷ.",
      "the_asteroid_belt_is_mostly_empty_spac": "Ṃōttan asteroid eo eḷaptata ej jikin ejjeḷọk! Tōḷọk ikōtaan asteroid ko ej milien km. Wa in mejatoto rej ilām im ejjeḷọk uwōta.",
      "not_always_saturn_is_95x_earth_s_mass_": "Jab iien otemjej! Saturn ej 95 alen eddoḷọk jān Laḷ ak gravity ioon ej 1.06g wōt kōnke eḷap im edik eddo eo an. Eddo ej pād ioon eddo IM depakpakin.",
      "all_parts_of_the_moon_receive_sunlight": "Aolep ṃōttan Allōñ rej bōk meram jān aḷ! \"Turin ettoḷọk\" ej jimattan eo jejjab maroñ loe jān Laḷ kōn tidal locking. Ej bōk joñan wōt aḷ.",
      "the_habitable_zone": "Bukwōn in Mour",
      "the_habitable_zone_or_goldilocks_zone_": "Bukwōn in mour (ak \"Goldilocks zone\") ej tōḷọk ko jān juon iju ijo dān emaroñ pād ioon juon planet. Ilo solar system eo ad, Venus ej pād ilo tōrerein lowaan, Laḷ ej pād ilo lukwōn, im Mars ej pād ilo tōrerein ālikin. Ak ñan dān, kwōj aikuj barāinwōt mejatoto im bukwōn magnet ejiṃwe!",
      "the_greenhouse_effect": "Greenhouse Effect",
      "when_sunlight_heats_a_planet_s_surface": "Ñe meram in aḷ ej kaōnḷọk ioon juon planet, ioon ej jilkinḷọk māāṇāṇ (infrared). Gas in greenhouse (CO₂, CH₄, H₂O) rej bōk māāṇāṇ in im bar jilkinḷọk, im kaōnḷọk planet eo. Greenhouse an Laḷ ej +33°C (ej lale mour). An Venus ej +510°C (ejjab bōjrak). Enañin ejjeḷọk an Mars (-60°C). Joñan gas in greenhouse ej kōṃṃan jeṃḷọken!",
      "magnetic_shields": "Likōkḷaḷ in Magnet",
      "a_planet_s_magnetic_field_creates_a_ma": "Bukwōn magnet an juon planet ej kōṃṃan juon \"magnetosphere\" — juon likōkḷaḷ jejjab loe eo ej kōjepḷaak kōto in aḷ (menin ewōr charge jān Aḷ). Magnetosphere an Laḷ ej kōjparok mejatoto eo ad im ej kōṃṃan bwe mour en maroñ. Mars ear luuji bukwōn magnet eo an 4 bilien iiō remootḷọk, im raar kotake mejatoto eo an ṃōkajḷọk. Magnetosphere an Jupiter ej 20,000 alen kajoorḷọk jān an Laḷ!",
      "why_isn_t_pluto_a_planet": "Etke Pluto Ejjab Juon Planet?",
      "in_2006_the_international_astronomical": "Ilo 2006, International Astronomical Union ear kōmeḷeḷeik jilu men ñan juon planet: (1) Ej doulul Aḷ ✓, (2) Ewōr an eddo ebwe ñan wāween doulul ✓, (3) Ear \"karreoiki iaḷ in doulul eo an\" jān menin ko jet ✗. Pluto ej jiṃor kōjerbal bukwōn in doulul eo an ippān tọujin menin ko an Kuiper Belt, kōn men in rej ba ej juon \"dwarf planet.\" Men in ejjab kadikḷọk an ekkā — New Horizons ear kwaḷọk bwe ej jerbal wōt!",
      "tidal_locking": "Tidal Locking",
      "over_billions_of_years_gravitational_t": "Ilo bilien iiō, kajoor in ibwijleplep an gravity emaroñ ruṃwijḷọk an juon allōñ ukōt ṃae iien ej jelṃae iien doulul eo an. Jeṃḷọken: juon turin ej jaḷḷọk ñan planet eo iien otemjej. Allōñ eo ad ej lokjak ippān Laḷ. Mercury ej lokjak jimattan ippān Aḷ (3:2). Pluto im Charon rej lokjak ippān doon — rej kwaḷọk turin eo wōt ñan doon iien otemjej!",
      "searching_for_life": "Ej pukot mour",
      "a_biosignature_is_any_evidence_of_past": "Juon biosignature ej jabdewōt kaṃool in mour ṃoktata ak kiiō. Ri-jeḷāḷọkjeṇ rej pukot: (1) dān, (2) molecule in organic, (3) gas ilo mejatoto āinwōt oxygen ak methane ko rejjab maroñ pād eḷaññe ejjeḷọk mour ej kōṃṃani, (4) jikin kajoor. Jikin eṃṃan tata ilo solar system eo ad: Mars (dān ṃor), Europa (lọjet iuṃwin kil), Enceladus (baib in dān), im Titan (ḷwe in methane).",
      "tour_guide": "Ri-tōl Ito-itak",
