      "explain_in_your_own_words": "Kōmeḷeḷeik kōn naan ko aṃ make...",
      "inquiry_widget_no_score_no_reveal_no_a": "Widget in kajjitōk — ejjeḷọk nōṃba, ejjeḷọk uwaak, ejjeḷọk kwaḷọk. T = √(a³/M) ekkar ñan Kepler III, M ilo eddo in aḷ, a ilo AU, T ilo iiō. Vis-viva ñan v ilo perihelion / aphelion.",
