      "all_8_planets_to_scale_size_orbit_watc": "Aolep 8 planet ilo joñan (depakpakin + doulul). Lale Mercury ej ettōr ipeḷaakin Aḷ ~4 alen ilo juon iiō in Laḷ. Planet ko lowaan rej epaake doon; ko ālikin rej doulul eḷap.",
      "kepler_i_orbits_are_ellipses": "Kepler I — doulul ko rej ellipse",
      "every_planet_orbits_in_an_ellipse_with": "Kajjojo planet ej doulul ilo juon ellipse im Aḷ ej pād ilo juon focus. Focus eo juon ej jikin ejjeḷọk. Doulul an Laḷ enañin jab jeplōklōk (e ≈ 0.017).",
      "kepler_ii_equal_areas_in_equal_times": "Kepler II — joñan ejja wōt ilo iien ejja wōt",
      "a_line_from_planet_to_sun_sweeps_equal": "Juon lain jān planet ñan Aḷ ej kalibubu joñan ejja wōt ilo iien ejja wōt — meḷeḷein bwe planet ej eṃṃakūt ṂŌKAJḶỌK epaake Aḷ (perihelion) im RUṂWIJḶỌK ettoḷọk (aphelion).",
      "kepler_iii_period_semi_major_axis": "Kepler III — iien² ∝ semi-major-axis³",
      "t_a_when_t_is_in_years_and_a_is_in_au_": "T² = a³ ñe T ej ilo iiō im a ej ilo AU. Laḷ T=1, a=1 ej kōṃṃan bwe bwini en pidodo. Eḷaññe kwōj ruoḷọk joñan doulul, iien ej ḷapḷọk ~2.83 alen.",
      "workshop_build_your_own_orbit": "Jikin jerbal — kalōk doulul eo aṃ make",
      "set_semi_major_axis_eccentricity_the_o": "Kajutak semi-major axis + eccentricity; orrery ej kwaḷọk doulul eo ilo iien lukkuun. Mālejjoñ e=0.9 — eñin jikin comet. Mālejjoñ e=0 — juon doulul ejiṃwe.",
      "hohmann_transfers_actual_rocket_math": "Hohmann transfer — bwini lukkuun an rocket",
      "the_minimum_energy_way_to_travel_betwe": "Iaḷ eo edikḷọk kajoor ñan ito-itak ikōtaan ruo doulul redoulul. Ruo kōkaan: diwōjḷọk jān doulul eo lowaan ilo perihelion in transfer, tōpar doulul eo ālikin ilo aphelion.",
      "challenges_apply_kepler_s_laws": "Kajjitōk — kōjerbal kien ko an Kepler",
      "multi_step_problems_predict_periods_fr": "Kajjitōk elōñ jekjek: ba iien jān semi-major axis, kile ṃōkaj in perihelion ippān aphelion, bwini Δv in transfer. AP Physics 1 + 2.",
      "true_false_concept_check": "Ṃool / Riab — etale ḷōmṇak",
      "quick_discrimination_quiz_on_common_ke": "Kajjitōk ṃōkaj kōn ḷōmṇak ko rebōd kōn Kepler. Ej jelṃae riab ko kōn doulul (\"epaak = ruṃwij,\" \"doulul ko rej doulul,\" \"aolep doulul rej etal ilo juon iaḷ\").",
      "kepler_inquiry_orbital_mechanics_sandb_2": "Kajjitōk an Kepler — jikin mālejjoñ orbital mechanics",
      "move_semi_major_axis_eccentricity_and_": "Eṃṃakūt semi-major axis, eccentricity, im eddo in menin eo ilo lukwōn. Ba wāween doulul eo — doulul, āinwōt lep, ejeplōklōk, āinwōt comet, parabolic. Ejjeḷọk nōṃba, ejjeḷọk uwaak.",
      "3d_mode_unresolved": "Wāween 3D Ejjab Tōprak",
      "webgl_failed_to_initialize_your_browse": "WebGL ear jab jino. Bōlen browser ak kein jerbal eo aṃ ejjab maroñ 3D hardware acceleration. Kwōj maroñ wōt kōjerbal wāween Orrery Lab ak bar kajjioñ.",
