      "in_1995_hubble_pointed_at_a_tiny_dark_": "Ilo 1995, Hubble ear jaḷḷọk ñan juon jikin edik emarok ilo mejatoto iuṃwin 10 raan. Jeṃḷọken: 3000 galaxy rettoḷọk ilo juon pija. JWST ear kōṃṃane eṃwilaḷḷọk, im ej katak kōn galaxy jān bukwi milien iiō ṃoktata ālikin Big Bang.",
      "star_color_temperature": "🌟 Kōḷōr + Māāṇāṇ in Iju",
      "hotter_stars_look_bluer_cooler_stars_r": "Iju ko remāāṇāṇḷọk rej bluuḷọk; iju ko reṃōḷoḷọk rej būrōrōḷọk. Rej kōkaḷḷe iju ko kōn OBAFGKM ekkar ñan spectral type.",
      "red_dwarf_coolest_most_common_stars_75": "Red dwarf — iju ko reṃōḷotata + elōñtata (75% in aolep iju)",
