      "best_naked_eye_observing_dark_site_awa": "Alwōj eṃṃantata kōn mejed: jikin emarok (ettoḷọk jān meram in jikin kweilọk), Allōñ iuṃwin mejatoto, mejed eṃōj aer minene (20-30 minit ilo marok). App ko ejjeḷọk oṇāer: Stellarium, SkyView, Star Walk rej jipañ kile ta ko kwōj loi.",
