      "carl_sagan_s_most_quoted_reflection_a_": "Ḷōmṇak eo eḷaptata aer eọroñ jān Carl Sagan. Juon pixel ewōr aolep ro jaar jeḷā kake.",
      "the_pale_blue_dot": "Tōbtōb eo Bluu Emeoeo",
      "from_this_distant_vantage_point_the_ea": "\"Jān jikin in ettoḷọk, Laḷ emaroñ jab āinwōt juon men eaorōk. Ak ñan kōj, ej āinjuon. Bar ḷōmṇak kōn tōbtōb eo. Eñin ijin. Eñin ṃweo iṃōd. Eñin kōj. Ioon aolep ro kwōj yokwe er, aolep ro kwōj jeḷā kajjier, aolep ro kwaar roñ kajjier, aolep armej raar mour, raar mour aer mour ie.\"",
