      "most_important_tool_dark_sky_light_pol": "Kein jerbal eḷaptata tokjān: mejatoto emarok. Meram eḷap ej jako kake 90% in iju ko. Katahdin Woods and Waters NM im AMC Maine Woods rej jikin International Dark Sky eṃōj kaṃooli; Acadia im Baxter barāinwōt ewōr aer mejatoto emarok eṃṃan.",
