      "maine_night_sky_by_season": "🌲 Mejatoto in Boñ ilo Maine ilo Kajjojo Iien",
      "maine_has_world_class_dark_skies_what_": "Maine ewōr an mejatoto emarok eṃṃantata ilo laḷ in. Ta eo kwōj pukot ilo kajjojo iien.",
      "maine_has_fantastic_dark_skies_especia": "Maine ewōr an mejatoto emarok eṃṃan otem ṃṃan — eḷaptata ilo eañ in jikin kweilọk ko. Katahdin Woods and Waters NM im AMC Maine Woods rej jikin International Dark Sky eṃōj kaṃooli; Acadia, Allagash, Baxter, im Cobscook barāinwōt relukkuun marok. Boñ ko ilo iien piọ reaetok + rekanooj alikkar.",
      "space_news_timeline": "📰 Iien ko ilo Nuuj in Mejatoto",
