      "utc_replaced_gmt_in_1972_based_on_atom": "UTC ear pinej jenkwan GMT ilo 1972. Ej pād ioon awa in atom ilo lab ko an aelōñ ipeḷaakin laḷ, im rej bwini lukwōn. Rej kobaik second ko ñe eaikuj.",
