      "wcag_contrast_checker_for_accessibilit": "Kein etale oktak in uno ekkar ñan WCAG bwe aolep ren maroñ lale",
      "educational_concepts": "💡 Ḷōmṇak in Katak",
      "color_theory_additive_vs_subtractive_m": "Ḷōmṇak in uno (kāreik ej kobaḷọk ippān kāreik ej bōkḷọk, uno ko rej jelṃae doon, HSL/RGB), lain ko rej ip jān bwinbwin (hypotrochoids, Lissajous), fractals im aer āinwōt doon, geometry in tessellation, ekōjkan mejed ej lo op art, kien in WCAG ñan aolep, im annañ jān kōmpiuta. Kajjojo kein jerbal ej katakin bwinbwin eo ilo lowaan aiboojoj eo.",
      "got_it_let_s_create": "Ijeḷā — jen kōṃṃan! 🎨",
