      "contrast_2": "Oktak in uno",
      "color_wheel_hsl_hsv_complementary_pair": "Wiiḷ in Uno — HSL/HSV + ruo uno rej jelṃae doon",
      "hue_0_360_around_the_wheel_saturation_": "Hue (0-360 ipeḷaakin wiiḷ eo), saturation (erreo in uno), lightness (meram). Ko rej jelṃae doon rej pād jabweoṇ, ko repaak doon rej pād iturin doon, ko triadic rej 120° jān doon. Newton ear likūt aolep uno ioon juon wiiḷ ilo 1666.",
      "color_mixer_subtractive_vs_additive": "Kein Kāreik Uno — bōkḷọk im kobaḷọk",
      "paint_and_print_subtractive_cmy_mixes_": "Uno im jeje ilo peba = bōkḷọk (CMY ej kāreik im erom marok); meram im jikin annañ = kobaḷọk (RGB ej kāreik im erom mouj). Ejja laḷ in wōt, ak bwinbwin ko rej kanooj oktak — juon printer ej ḷōmṇak kōn plate K, juon TV ej ḷōmṇak kōn Hz.",
      "pixel_art_bitmap_craft_at_8_8_to_32_32": "Annañ Pixel — jerbal in bitmap ilo 8×8 ñan 32×32",
      "each_pixel_is_a_deliberate_decision_ne": "Kajjojo pixel ej juon pepe eṃōj ḷōmṇak kake. Sprites in NES rar likūt juon ri-kajoor ilo 16×16 ippān emān wōt uno. Algorithm in lain eo an Bresenham ej jeje lain ko rej jitpeeḷeḷ im ejjab kōjerbal nōṃba ko reṃōttan.",
      "symmetry_reflection_rotation_glide": "Jokkun wōt juon — kilaj, dāpilpil, im jirilọk",
      "bilateral_mirror_rotational_n_fold_poi": "Ruo rājet (kilaj), dāpilpil (n-fold), im juon point. 17 kumi in wallpaper rej kōkḷaḷ aolep wāween 2D ko rej bar wanṃaanḷọk — aolep jerbal ko an Escher.",
      "spirograph_hypotrochoid_roulettes": "Spirograph — roulettes in hypotrochoid",
      "a_small_circle_rolls_inside_a_big_one_": "Juon doulul edik ej dāpilpil ilowaan juon eḷap, im pen eo ej ettoḷọk jān lukwōn. Ratio in ruo radius ej kile joñan wūt ko; ettoḷọk in pen eo ej kile mijel eo. Kein ikkure eṇ eṃōj patent e ilo 1965, ak bwinbwin eo ear itok jān 1700 ko.",
      "generative_algorithm_randomness_as_art": "Kōṃṃan make — algorithm + men ko rejjab jeḷā rej ri-kōṃṃan annañ",
      "sol_lewitt_wrote_instructions_the_wall": "Sol LeWitt ear jeje naan in kaiñi wōt; ri-jerbal eo ioon kiin eṃ ear kōṃṃane. Rainin: Processing, p5.js, Cinder. “Ri-kōṃṃan annañ eo ej kien eo, ejjab tōprak eo.”",
      "spin_art_centripetal_physics_in_paint": "Annañ in Dāpilpil — physics in kañūrñūr ñan lukwōn ilo uno",
      "drop_paint_spin_watch_it_fling_outward": "Kabōjrak uno, kadāpilpil, im lale ekōjkan an kālọk ñan nabōj ilo wāween ip. Damien Hirst ear bōk millian ko jān wia annañ in dāpilpil. Ejja physics eo wōt in juon kein kaṃōrā salad; F = mω²r.",
      "string_art_curves_from_straight_lines": "Annañ in To — lain ko rej ip jān lain ko rejiṃwe",
      "connect_every_n_th_nail_an_envelope_cu": "Koba kajjojo dila kein ka N; juon lain envelope ej waḷọk. Mary Everest Boole ear kwaḷọk men in ñan kilaaj in bwinbwin ilo 1900. Cardioid eo jān lain ko rejiṃwe ej ṃool in kaṃōṇōṇō.",
      "op_art_fooling_the_visual_system": "Op Art — ṃoṇe wāween ad lale",
      "bridget_riley_s_moir_fields_vasarely_s": "Jikin moiré ko an Bridget Riley, grid ko an Vasarely. Cell ko ilo mejed rej lo ṃakūtkūt rej kanooj jerbal ñe oktak in uno ej kōṃṃakūt ṃōkaj — peij eo ej āinwōt *ej ṃakūtkūt*.",
      "tessellation_the_17_wallpaper_groups": "Tessellation — 17 kumi in wallpaper",
      "every_periodic_2d_tiling_fits_one_of_1": "Aolep tiling 2D ko rej bar wanṃaanḷọk rej tōpar juon iaan 17 kumi in jokkun wōt juon. Escher ear lo men in ke ear ilọk ñan Alhambra ilo 1936; innām ear kōjerbal 30 iiō ñan kōmate aolep.",
      "fractal_self_similar_at_every_scale": "Fractal — ej āinwōt e make ilo aolep joñan",
      "mandelbrot_1975_cauliflower_coastlines": "Mandelbrot 1975. Cauliflower, tōrerein āne, iaḷ in bōtōktōk, jarom, im jikin mennin emmenono — aolep rej fractal. “Kōdọ ko rejjab bọọḷ, toḷ ko rejjab kōn, im kilin wōjke ejjab meṇoknok.”",
      "gradient_smooth_color_transitions": "Gradient — oktak in uno ejjeḷọk kabōjrak",
      "css_gives_you_linear_radial_and_conic_": "CSS ej lewōj gradient linear, radial, im conic. Iiaḷ in kōdọ ko reṃool ewōr aolep uno ejjeḷọk kōjepel (ejjeḷọk ṃōttan rekōjenolọk) — “7 uno in iiaḷ in kōdọ” ear pepe eo an Newton kōn unin al.",
      "stereogram_3d_from_a_flat_page": "Stereogram — 3D jān juon peij eppāt",
      "90s_magic_eye_craze_each_eye_sees_a_sl": "Iien Magic Eye ilo 90 ko. Kajjojo mej ej lo juon annañ eṃōj an ṃakūtkūt jidik; eḷaññe kwōj kōṃṃan bwe mejaṃ ren jelṃae ak ren jepel jiṃwe, ḷōmṇak eo aṃ ej koba er ñan ṃwilaḷ. Ilo ṃool 5% in armej rejjab maroñ lo e — ejjab bōd eo aer.",
      "contrast_wcag_4_5_1_3_1_apca": "Oktak in uno — WCAG 4.5:1 / 3:1 / APCA",
      "wcag_2_1_normal_text_4_5_1_large_3_1_w": "WCAG 2.1: jeje edik 4.5:1, jeje eḷap 3:1. Unin an oktak edik in uno kōṃṃan apañ ñan ro emō an lale, meñe kwe kwōmaroñ riiti. APCA (eo ej itok ālikin WCAG 3.0) ej kōjerbal meram āinwōt mejed ej loe, ejjab ratio in luminance wōt.",
      "harmony_lab_title": "Kokkeitaak — ainikien, ratio, im uno",
      "harmony_lab_hint": "Keidi interval ko rej errā im ko rejjab errā, koba ratio in frequency ippān wāween, im ukōt kōtaan al ñan kokkeitaak ilo lale.",
