      "canvas_summary_business_empty": "Jikin lale in peejnej ejjañin obrak. Jino juon peejnej ilaḷ bwe kwōn lo ṃani, buñbuñ, im orḷọk in raan ijin.",
      "canvas_summary_macro": "Jikin lale in ekonomi in aelōñ ej kwaḷọk eddekḷọk in GDP, orḷọk in oṇāān, oṇāān ṃuri, ejjeḷọk jerbal, joñak in wia, im bwebwenato in karōk.",
      "canvas_summary_inquiry": "Wāween kajjitōk in karōk ej kōjerbal emān kein tōbtōb in karōk bwe en kwaḷọk juon jelōt makro in katak. Kōjerbal baar in karōk ko ilaḷ bwe kwōn keidi oktak in GDP, orḷọk in oṇāān, im ejjeḷọk jerbal.",
      "teacher_prompt_supply_demand": "Kajjitōk ippān ri-jikuuḷ ro bwe ren ba ṃokta eḷaññe oṇāān, joñan, ḷapḷọk, ak iietḷọk enaaj oktak, ṃokta jān aer tōbtōb juon kein tōbtōb.",
      "teacher_prompt_personal_finance": "Kajjitōk ippān ri-jikuuḷ ro bwe ren kwaḷọk juon men eṃōj kōtḷọke ilo karōk ṃani eo, im juon un etke orḷọk kobaḷọk ej leḷọk ṃōṇōṇō ñan ro rej jino ṃokta.",
      "teacher_prompt_stock_market": "Kajjitōk ippān ri-jikuuḷ ro bwe ren kōjenolọk ilo juon wōt kōmeḷeḷe: eṃṃakūt in oṇāān, kajoor in peejnej eo, im kauwōtata in kobban ṃōttan ko.",
      "teacher_prompt_entrepreneur": "Kajjitōk ippān ri-jikuuḷ ro bwe ren watōk jete kab ren aikuj wiakake bwe ren tōpar ijo eṃōj kōḷḷā aolep oṇāān ie, ṃokta jān aer kapeḷḷọk peejnej eo ñan raan eo.",
      "teacher_prompt_macro": "Kajjitōk ippān ri-jikuuḷ ro bwe ren kāālōt juon mejānkajjik in karōk im kwaḷọk kein joñe eo enaaj kwaḷọk eṃṃan ak nana.",
      "teacher_prompt_inquiry": "Kajjitōk ippān ri-jikuuḷ ro kein tōbtōb in karōk ta eo ri-meḷeḷe in ekonomi rej jumae doon kake eḷaptata, innem ren kōmeḷeḷeik etke men in ej juon wōt kein jipañ katak.",
