      "demand_slopes_down_cheap_buy_more_supp": "Lain in kōṇaan ej wanlaḷḷọk (edik oṇāān = eḷapḷọk aer wia); lain in leḷọk ej wanlōñḷọk (eḷap oṇāān = eḷapḷọk aer kōṃṃan). Oṇāān im joñan in iioon ej ijo rej kijoone doon ie. Bok eo an Adam Smith ilo 1776, Wealth of Nations, ej ḷoñtak eo wōt.",
