      "revenue_costs_profit_break_even_point_": "Ṃani ej deḷọñ − oṇāān = orḷọk. Ijo eṃōj kōḷḷā aolep oṇāān ie ej ñe eṃōj kōḷḷā oṇāān ko rejjab oktak. Elōñ peejnej ko re-dik rej buñ ilo iiō eo kein ka 5; ro rej mour wōt raar lo ṃweiuk ko ṃakete ej kōṇaan. Oṇāān bōktok juon ri-wia (CAC) ippān oṇāān an ri-wia eo iuṃwin aolepen iien (LTV) ej bwini eo an ri-jino ilo raan otemjej.",
