      "policy_inquiry_hero_hint": "Ṃakūtkūt kein tōbtōb ko, ba ṂOKTA ewi wāween ekonomi enaaj pād ie ṃokta jān aṃ riiti, innem kwaḷọk unin aṃ ḷōmṇak. Ri-meḷeḷe in ekonomi ro reṃool rej lukkuun jumae doon kōn kōkḷaḷ im joñan kein.",
      "try_supply_demand": "Kajjioñ: likūt Jabōn Oṇāān Ilōñ ñan $30 (kōṃadṃōd oṇāān in reent). Ba ṃokta — jete ṃōttan enaaj iietḷọk ilo ṃakete eo?",
      "try_personal_finance": "Kajjioñ: likūt 15% ilo Balanced im kāālōt jikin jokwe eo Ri-jokwe Ippaṃ. Lale aolepen ṃweiuk ippān ṃani iuṃwin 5 iiō.",
      "try_stock_market": "Kajjioñ: wia im wiakake iuṃwin 5 raan, innem keidi orḷọk eo aṃ ippān taal in Index (dāpij). Wōn ej anjọ?",
